Elite Disaster Response Team - Volcano - Ludum Dare 50

requirements_en.minimum:
Minimum:
  • Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system
  • OS: Windows 7 (SP1+) 64-bit or Windows 10 64-bit
  • Processor: Intel i3-2100 / AMD FX-4130
  • Memory: 2 GB RAM
  • Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GT 1030 / AMD Radeon RX 550
  • DirectX: Version 11
  • Network: Broadband Internet connection
requirements_en.recommended:
Recommended:
  • Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system
  • OS: Windows 10 64-bit
  • Processor: Intel i3-2100 / AMD FX-4130
  • Memory: 4 GB RAM
  • Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GT 1030 / AMD Radeon RX 550
  • DirectX: Version 11
  • Network: Broadband Internet connection
